    {
      "author": "Scott Godin",
      "text": "It's also impossible to change the number of channels in the audio recording after recording has started, without re-writting it.",
      "time": "2026-07-22T12:17:25.000Z"
    },
    {
      "author": "Scott Godin",
      "text": "Think 3rd party joins later in the call.",
      "time": "2026-07-22T12:17:52.000Z"
    },
    {
      "author": "Scott Godin",
      "text": "Instead of reusing Dialog - we could consider a more generic concept if a dialog-set or dialog-group.",
      "time": "2026-07-22T12:22:53.000Z"
    },
    {
      "author": "Scott Godin",
      "text": "if->of",
      "time": "2026-07-22T12:23:24.000Z"
    },
    {
      "author": "Scott Godin",
      "text": "There are cases where a call will have multiple recordings.",
      "time": "2026-07-22T12:33:20.000Z"
    },
    {
      "author": "Scott Godin",
      "text": "So solving with channels only isn't really possible.",
      "time": "2026-07-22T12:33:38.000Z"
    },
    {
      "author": "Edward Guy,",
      "text": "Anyone else getting static on audio?",
      "time": "2026-07-22T12:34:44.000Z"
    },
    {
